        {
            "_id": "1BwV9TFJ4LsBz1jc",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Conflagration of Jaws",
            "sort": 1000000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The hellfire hydra slams each of its heads into the ground, where they explode before quickly reforming. The hellfire hydra creates a number of @Template[type:burst|distance:5]s within 10 feet equal to its current number of heads. These bursts can't overlap. Each creature in a burst takes @Damage[6d6[fire]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:40|basic] save). This counts as a number of attacks equal to the number of heads the hellfire hydra has toward the hydra's multiple attack penalty.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
